race.comment: Hard to go past SHAME ON SUE (7) who has placed at both runs this time in. Raced on speed latest in richer company and expected to give a sight again. MISS GOSSIP GIRL (6) has been mixing form and is much better than the last two. Spotted a big start last time and was beaten a long way. This far easier and on best figures in right in the mix. PIERRE LE QUILL (10) resumed from a break with a fair run in tougher company. Fitter for it and well placed this time. Looks a strong winning hope. ALESUND (1) was thereabouts in a similar race last time. Overdue for a win and among the hopes on last run. DALENTINO (5) wasn't beaten far fresh and strips fitter. Has the claim and worth including.
